# 百分比布局


```html
<section>
    <div></div>
    <div></div>
</section>
```

```css
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

section {
    width: 100%;
    /* 一般会设置一个范围，避免变形 */
    max-width: 980px;
    min-width: 320px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

section div {
    float: left;
    width: 50%;
    height: 400px;
}

section div:nth-child(1) {
    background-color: pink;
}

section div:nth-child(2) {
    background-color: purple;
}
```
